          "description": "\u003csection class=\"text-center\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 class=\"subheadline\"\u003eHow Local Manufacturing at Purity Park Ensures Radical Integrity\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cem class=\"block post-date\"\u003ePosted on March 19, 2026\u003c\/em\u003e \u003cem class=\"block post-by\"\u003eWritten by: 100% PURE\u003csup\u003e®\u003c\/sup\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"additions\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/section\u003e\n\u003csection\u003e\n\u003carticle\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"grid\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"grid__item large--one-whole\"\u003e\n\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"m-v\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0648\/1955\/files\/Cover_photo_Made_in_San_Jose__Why__Where__Matters_as_Much_as__What.webp?v=1773416662\" alt=\"Cover_photo_Made_in_San_Jose__Why__Where__Matters_as_Much_as__What\"\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch3 class=\"m-v text-center h3\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIntroduction: The Gold Standard of \"Made in Our Own Lab\"\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eIn the age of global outsourcing, the label \"Made in the USA\" has become a baseline requirement for many. It offers a sense of comfort, but it rarely tells the whole story. Most beauty brands—even the most expensive \"clean\" names—do not make their own products. They send a purchase order to an outside lab, essentially renting space and time in a facility that might be making a harsh floor cleaner or a generic body wash on the very same equipment the day before.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eAt 100% PURE, we believe that true purity cannot be outsourced. We believe that if you don’t own the facility, you don’t own the standard.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eIntroduce Purity Park in San Jose, CA. This isn’t just a warehouse or a fulfillment center; it is the physical spine of our brand. It is an ISO-certified sanctuary where our \"Science-Backed Purity\" transforms from a concept into a tangible reality. By owning the facility where the science happens, we eliminate the \"Knowledge Gap\" between the formulator’s dream and the final bottle on your vanity. We aren't just a marketing company that sells skincare; we are a laboratory that engineers health.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"m-v text-center h3\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eThe Silicon Valley Halo: Precision Skincare Engineering\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eSan Jose is more than just a city; it is the heart of Silicon Valley—a global hub of technical excellence and innovation. By anchoring our manufacturing here, we benefit from what we call the \"Silicon Valley Halo.\" This is the environment of precision, high safety standards, and rigorous testing that defines the region’s high-tech industry.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\u003cb\u003ePharmaceutical-Grade vs. \"Kitchen Chemistry\"\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eMany smaller clean brands operate on a model of \"kitchen chemistry.\" While their intentions are good, their environments often lack the \"Spine\" of clinical rigor. Our San Jose facility is equipped with pharmaceutical-grade clean rooms. These are controlled environments where the air is filtered, the temperature is stabilized, and the risk of cross-contamination is virtually zero.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eThis technical excellence is what allows us to master \"Frequency A\" skincare—the \"Clean \u0026amp; Quiet\" frequency. This frequency focuses on restoration and barrier health. To create products that are truly quiet and non-irritating, the manufacturing environment must be perfectly controlled. You cannot achieve \"restorative\" results if your formula is fighting microscopic impurities from a shared production line.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\u003cb\u003eThe Strategic Advantage of Local Oversight\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eBeing local means our R\u0026amp;D team and our production team share the same roof. When Susie Wang or Dr. Cody Chalker, PhD, designs a \"Wise Skin\" formula, they can walk onto the floor and oversee the very first batch. We can adjust the mixing speed, the cooling temperature, and the stabilization process in real-time. This level of strategic pragmatism ensures that the formula we promise is the exact formula you receive. We don't have to guess if our standards were met; we enforce them with our own eyes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"m-v text-center h3\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eVertical Integration: Protecting the Chain of Custody\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eIn the world of supply chain management, the \"Chain of Custody\" refers to the chronological documentation of the movement and handling of a product. Most beauty brands lose control of this chain the moment their ingredients arrive at a third-party factory.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\u003cb\u003eControlling Every Touchpoint\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eAt 100% PURE, we practice full Vertical Integration. From the moment the raw Seaberry fruit is harvested and arrives at our doors to the second the finished moisturizer is sealed, we control every single touchpoint. This is the cornerstone of our Radical Integrity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eBecause we own the facility, we eliminate the risk of \"hidden fillers\" or the accidental inclusion of toxins that can occur in third-party facilities that process thousands of different formulas. We don't have to worry about whether the equipment was cleaned to our exacting standards—we are the ones cleaning it. This allows us to offer a toxin-free guarantee that is defensible and absolute.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\u003cb\u003eEnforcing Purity through Sovereignty\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eBy maintaining sovereignty over our production, we move from \"Passive Purity\" (hoping the lab followed our rules) to a state of being \"Scientifically Superior.\" We don't just \"source\" our products; we architect them. This level of control is why we can confidently offer products that are MOCRA-compliant and meet the highest safety standards in the world. We lead with the \"Mind\" proof of our owned manufacturing, so your \"Heart\" can feel safe using our products.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"m-v text-center h3\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eThe San Jose Standard in Your Ritual\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eTo see the impact of our San Jose manufacturing, one only needs to experience \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.100percentpure.com\/collections\/the-sensitive-skin-strength-ritual\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eThe Sensitive-Skin Strength Ritual\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.100percentpure.com\/collections\/the-sensitive-skin-strength-ritual\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e.\u003c\/a\u003e These five products are the primary beneficiaries of our \"Small-Batch\" and \"Cold-Processing\" methodologies at Purity Park.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e1.\u003c\/b\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.100percentpure.com\/products\/calendula-flower-cleansing-milk\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eCalendula Flower Cleansing Milk\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e\n\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eThe San Jose Difference:\u003c\/b\u003e This cleanser is freshly batched to preserve the delicate botanical extracts of the calendula flower. In a massive third-party facility, these delicate hydrosols are often subjected to high-heat pipes and long storage times, which can degrade their calming properties. In our lab, we use \"Quiet Science\" to ensure the calendula remains restorative and vibrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e2.\u003c\/b\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.100percentpure.com\/products\/matcha-oat-face-scrub\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eMatcha Oat Face Scrub\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u0026amp; 3.\u003c\/b\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.100percentpure.com\/products\/matcha-oat-milk-nourishing-mask\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eMatcha Oat Milk Nourishing Mask\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e\n\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eThe San Jose Difference:\u003c\/b\u003e Colloidal oats are highly sensitive to moisture and texture changes. By utilizing small-batch blending, we ensure that these products maintain their signature \"hug-like\" texture. Our solar-powered facility allows us to process the matcha at precise temperatures, ensuring the antioxidants are stabilized and ready to protect your skin from the \"noise\" of the environment.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e4.\u003c\/b\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.100percentpure.com\/products\/intensive-nourishing-facial-oil\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIntensive Nourishing Facial Oil\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u0026amp; 5.\u003c\/b\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.100percentpure.com\/products\/seaberry-moisturizer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eSeaberry Moisturizer\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e\n\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eThe San Jose Difference:\u003c\/b\u003e These are the pinnacle of our stabilization and dermal delivery engineering. Because these formulas contain rare Omegas and Vitamin E, they are highly prone to oxidation. Under the direct supervision of our San Jose R\u0026amp;D team, these products are vacuum-sealed and cold-processed. This ensures that the \"liquid gold\" of the Seaberry stays fresh and active, providing maximum \u003cb\u003edermal absorption\u003c\/b\u003e the moment it hits your skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"m-v text-center h3\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eConclusion: \"Where\" Is a Safety Feature\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eIn the future of beauty, transparency is no longer optional. At 100% PURE, we believe that the most important thing we can tell you is not just what is in the bottle, but who made it and where.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eBy staying local in San Jose and remaining vertically integrated, we are not just making skincare; we are protecting a legacy of Science-Backed Purity. \"Where\" your skincare is made is not just a geographic fact—it is a safety feature. It is the guarantee that your products were made with radical integrity, scientific precision, and a deep respect for your skin's health.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eWe invite you to trust in our process and our history. We have been engineering pure beauty since 2004, and we stand by every drop with our Happy Promise: If you don’t love your results within 60 days, we’ll take it back. Pure and simple. We gladly offer an exchange or refund on gently used products within 60 days of purchase from 100percentpure.com (minus shipping costs).\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"m-v text-center h3\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eFAQ Section: The Power of Purity Park\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eWhy does 100% PURE manufacture its own products?\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eWe manufacture our own products to ensure total control over safety, stability, and ingredient quality. Most brands outsource their production, which creates a \"Knowledge Gap\" and increases the risk of contamination or diluted standards. By owning Purity Park, we can guarantee that every formula meets our rigorous Science-Backed Purity standards.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eWhat are the benefits of \"small-batch\" skincare?\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eSmall-batch skincare allows for fresher ingredients and higher nutrient potency. In large-scale industrial manufacturing, products are often made in massive quantities and sit in warehouses for months. At our San Jose facility, we make smaller, more frequent batches. This means fewer harsh stabilizers are needed, and the botanical extracts stay at their biological peak when they reach your vanity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow does local manufacturing help the environment?\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003eLocal manufacturing at Purity Park significantly reduces our carbon footprint. Having our R\u0026amp;D, manufacturing, and fulfillment in a central hub reduces the transit needed between different stages of production. We also maintain strict local oversight of our ethical and environmental standards, ensuring we are as kind to the planet as we are to your skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"m-v\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eExperience the power of owned science. Experience \u003c\/em\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cem\u003e100% PURE\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cem\u003e.\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/article\u003e\n\u003c\/section\u003e",
